The '''Bothan Independent Treasury''' was the central financial institution of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. It stored its collateral on [[Aargau/Legends|Aargau]] to avoid local interference. Following the collapse of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], the Treasury was centralized as part of the [[Combined Bothan Clans|Bothan Council]].

